URL(path) ->component -> load file -> html/template used in component and  JS -> API -> SQL database -> response -> data -> VUE -> html

here, the url you entered is the path by which the component is called. The component consist of html template and script(JS). 
The template is simply a markup language enclosed in tags and template. And script(JS) request using AXIOS library using http 
request like get, post, put , delete and add. The request from JS to Database has a bridge or connection established by API. The API
configure the access to database and when database request matches the response is send to VUE data and show in HTML as designed.
